# APEX OMEGA v3+

Institutional trading signal engine.

Features:

• Multi-timeframe market analysis  
• SMT twin-pair divergence detection  
• Liquidity trap detection  
• Order block intelligence  
• AI probability scoring  
• Liquidity map targeting  
• Volatility regime filter  
• Automatic stop loss and take profit generation  
• 20+ market monitoring  
• Cloud deployment  

Signals are sent automatically via webhook alerts.
